    "title": "Tech Mahindra Holdings Services is Hiring: Full Stack Developer (Principal)",
    "description": "Tech Mahindra Holdings Services has an exciting opening for a Full Stack Developer at our Agra office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Tech Mahindra Holdings Services:\nTech Mahindra Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in React\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Agra, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tech Mahindra Holdings Services!",
